  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Tutorial_GM_AfterCauldron
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - Good. Now we need air.
  - Yes, I know, air is all around us. But we need a way to gather it before we can fuse with it.
  - An old windmill stands outside your lab. Set it turning, and the wind is yours. Press Space to jump any ledge or fence that gets in your way.
